llvm dialect PRs

- https://github.com/xdslproject/xdsl/pull/5683
- https://github.com/xdslproject/xdsl/pull/5684

exo dialect PRs

- https://github.com/xdslproject/xdsl/pull/4371
    - needs to be redone
    - attempts to add lowering for `memref.reinterpret_cast` and `memref.cast` in the upstream `convert-memref-to-ptr` pass
    - `memref.subview`: https://mlir.llvm.org/docs/Dialects/MemRef/#memrefsubview-memrefsubviewop
    - `memref.reinterpret_cast`: https://mlir.llvm.org/docs/Dialects/MemRef/#memrefreinterpret_cast-memrefreinterpretcastop

long term goal

- exo emits LLVM IR (not just c)
- xdsl gets proper memref descriptor support
- compile exo → xdsl → llvmlite and benchmark real workloads
